PN,42401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773857158
OL,3,CCould a win for Newcastle in Barcelona
OL,4,Cbe their biggest football achievement?
OL,6,FNewcastle United's Champions League
OL,7,Ffirst leg hero Harvey Barnes was
OL,8,Fsurrounded by journalists and camera
OL,9,Fcrews in the mixed zone at St James'
OL,10,FPark last week.
OL,12,FHe discussed his goal in the one-all
OL,13,Fdraw and assessed his team's chances
OL,14,Fin the return leg in Barcelona. He was
OL,15,Fasked whether the Magpies actually
OL,16,Fbelieved they could go to the Camp Nou
OL,17,Fand win the tie.
OL,19,F"Why not?" was his reply.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
