PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773857158
OL,3,CCould a win for Newcastle in Barcelona
OL,4,Cbe their biggest football achievement?
OL,6,FWhy not indeed? Let's try and answer
OL,7,Fthat question. Why can't Eddie Howe's
OL,8,Fteam actually pull this off?
OL,10,FThe answer the majority of the
OL,11,Ffootball world would give you is
OL,12,Fsomething along the lines of "because
OL,13,Fthey're Barcelona and you're Newcastle
OL,14,FUnited". Because they've got Lamine
OL,15,FYamal and Pedri and half a dozen
OL,16,Fgenuine A-Listers and because they're
OL,17,Fjust bigger, better, shinier and
OL,18,Fsexier than the boys in Black and
OL,19,FWhite.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773857158
OL,3,CCould a win for Newcastle in Barcelona
OL,4,Cbe their biggest football achievement?
OL,6,FThe majority might well be right. If
OL,7,Fboth teams play as well as they can,
OL,8,FBarcelona will probably win. But is
OL,9,Fthere a little too much acceptance of
OL,10,Fthis status quo? A bit too much
OL,11,F"Barcelona will get through because
OL,12,FBarcelona always gets through"?
OL,14,FCertainly that's what UEFA expects and
OL,15,Fwants. They want the big beasts of
OL,16,FEuropean Football lining up in the
OL,17,FChampions League quarter-finals and
OL,18,Fbeyond.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773857158
OL,3,CCould a win for Newcastle in Barcelona
OL,4,Cbe their biggest football achievement?
OL,6,FBut Eddie Howe's Newcastle are
OL,7,Fdisruptors. They are inconsistent
OL,8,Fdisruptors, for sure, but on any given
OL,9,Fday they can beat any given team. They
OL,10,Fare dangerous in this scenario.
OL,12,FDon't Newcastle United's strength's
OL,13,Fprey on Barcelona's weaknesses? At
OL,14,Fleast a little bit?
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
