FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773857158
OL,3,CCould a win for Newcastle in Barcelona
OL,4,Cbe their biggest football achievement?
OL,6,FThe Magpies will be fast, aggressive,
OL,7,Fbelligerent and make life physically
OL,8,Fhard for their opponents. Barcelona
OL,9,Fwill defend with a high line and will
OL,10,Fhave complete confidence they can play
OL,11,Ftheir way around any press and find a
OL,12,Fway out of any difficult situation.
OL,13,FThey will take risks. There are
OL,14,Fpossibilities there for Eddie Howe and
OL,15,Fhis team.
OL,17,FFrom 1997 to 2001 to 2026 - Could
OL,18,FNewcastle United's visit to Barcelona
OL,19,Fin the Champions League be third time
OL,20,Flucky?
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
