PN,42406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773857158
OL,3,CCould a win for Newcastle in Barcelona
OL,4,Cbe their biggest football achievement?
OL,6,FThink of the first leg and how well
OL,7,FNewcastle played. How they knocked
OL,8,FBarcelona completely out of rhythm.
OL,9,FThink of how Newcastle played in their
OL,10,Fwin at Chelsea on Saturday night.
OL,12,FFast, streetwise and defensively
OL,13,Fresolute in the face of a bunch of
OL,14,Fmoody creative types. That's the
OL,15,Fblueprint for Barcelona right there.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773857158
OL,3,CCould a win for Newcastle in Barcelona
OL,4,Cbe their biggest football achievement?
OL,6,FBut look, it won't be easy. Barca's
OL,7,Fhigh-end talent is just better than
OL,8,FNewcastle's. Barcelona have home
OL,9,Fadvantage, and the new look Spotify
OL,10,FCamp Nou is a pretty big home
OL,11,Fadvantage.
OL,13,FThat last gasp equaliser in the first
OL,14,Fleg was a serious gut punch for the
OL,15,FMagpies. If they brought a first leg
OL,16,Flead to the Camp Nou, you could
OL,17,Fdefinitely see them finishing the job.
OL,18,FGoing there on level terms? It's a
OL,19,Flong shot.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773857158
OL,3,CCould a win for Newcastle in Barcelona
OL,4,Cbe their biggest football achievement?
OL,6,FBut a year ago this week Eddie Howe's
OL,7,Fteam won a cup final they weren't
OL,8,Fsupposed to win. Knocking Barcelona
OL,9,Fout of the Champions League wouldn't
OL,10,Fresonate throughout Tyneside history
OL,11,Fas much as that Carabao Cup victory,
OL,12,Fbut it would arguably be a bigger
OL,13,Ffootball achievement.
OL,15,FBut can they really do it? Really?
OL,17,FAs Harvey says, "Why not?"
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
